                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170521-57-off285 t18170521-57-cd286"></join>, one watch, value 5l.; one watch chain value 30s.; one seal, value 2l.; and one key, value 1l., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170521-57-victim400" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
